<http://dx.doi.org/10.3897/phytokeys.235.111400.figure4>
    dc:description "Figure 4. Curcuma rubroaurantiaca Skornick. & Soonthornk. at the type locality A habit B inflorescence with detail of flower in front view C detail of leaf sheaths and ligules D rhizome E inflorescence with detail of flower in side view F two flowers and dissected flower (from left: ovary with epigynous glands, calyx, floral tube (dissected longitudinally), upper row dorsal and lateral corolla lobes and stamen, lower row lateral staminodes and labellum G stamen from front, back and side view. All from the type collection, Soonthornkalump Sutt- 242. Photographed by Sutthinut Soonthornkalump." ;
    fabio:hasRepresentation "https://binary.pensoft.net/fig/939875" ;
    a fabio:Figure .

